The Yommi tree is a tree grown during Legends' Quest in the Kharazi Jungle. It is grown from yommi tree seeds and then chopped down and carved to create the yommi totem.

The tree progresses through 3 growth stages. The tree starts out as a baby, then grows to a sapling and finally an adult. Once grown, it can be felled and then trimmed. The tree may also die or become rotten if not carved quickly.

Chopping a dead yommi tree occasionally produces Magic logs. This is a possible way to obtain magic logs without needing 75 Woodcutting, 58 Hunter to catch nature implings, or melee stats to do slayer.

The '''Yommi tree''' is a tree grown during [[Legends' Quest]] in the [[Kharazi Jungle]]. It is grown from [[yommi tree seeds]] and then chopped down and carved to create the [[yommi totem]].

The tree progresses through 3 growth stages. The tree starts out as a baby, then grows to a sapling and finally an adult. Once grown, it can be felled and then trimmed. The tree may also die or become rotten if not carved quickly.

Chopping a dead yommi tree occasionally produces [[Magic logs]]. This is a possible way to obtain magic logs without needing 75 Woodcutting, 58 Hunter to catch [[nature implings]], or melee stats to do slayer.
